name: Database of Latin Dictionaries
description: Provides access to the following dictionaries:Albert Blaise, Dictionnaire latin-français des auteurs chrétiens; Firminus Verris Dictionarius, Dictionnaire latin-français de Firmin Le Ver, ed. by B. Merrilees and W. Edwards; and C. du Fresne ('du Cange'), Glossarium ad scriptores mediae et infimae latinitatis.
